1. e4 {[%mdl 1] Duras was awarded the first beauty prize (150 Kronen) 1.Schönheitspreis für Duras (150 Kronen).} e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Bb5 Nf6 4. d3 Bc5 5. Be3 Bxe3 6. fxe3 O-O (6... Ne7) 7. O-O $5 d5 8. Nc3 d4 9. Bxc6 bxc6 10. exd4 exd4 11. Ne2 Ng4 12. Qd2 Qd6 {Black has the initiative.} (12... c5) 13. h3 $5 Ne3 $1 14. Rf2 c5 15. c3 f5 16. cxd4 fxe4 (16... cxd4 17. Nfxd4 f4 18. Rc1) 17. Qxe3 $1 exf3 $1 18. dxc5 Qc6 $2 {[#]} 19. Rxf3 $1 {Duras plays a spectacular move.} Bb7 20. Rg3 Rae8 21. Qd4 Qh6 22. Nc3 $1 Rd8 23. Qb4 $1 Bc6 24. Ne4 Rf4 25. Re1 Rdf8 26. Kh2 $3 {Le Lionnais called this game Jiu Jitsu.} {The pointe is} Qh4 27. Qb3+ Kh8 28. Ng5 R4f5 (28... Bxg2 29. Nf7+ Kg8 30. Kxg2 R4xf7 31. Rf1) 29. Ne6 Rg8 30. Qc3 Rf6 31. Ng5 Rgf8 32. Rg4 Rf2 33. Ne4 Qh6 {prevents the next combination.} {Not} 34. Nxf2 $2 Rxf2 35. Re6 Rf6 36. Rxc6 Rxc6 $1 37. Qd4 $1 Qf6 38. Rf4 {gains a small advantage.} Qe7 39. Qd7 1-0


