1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 e6 3. Nc3 Bb4 4. Qc2 d5 (4... Nc6) 5. a3 Bxc3+ 6. Qxc3 Ne4 7. Qc2 c5 (7... Nc6 8. e3 e5 9. cxd5 Qxd5 10. Bc4 Qa5+ 11. b4 Nxb4 12. Qxe4 Nc2+ 13. Ke2 Qe1+ 14. Kf3 Nxa1 15. Bb2 Be6 16. d5 O-O-O 17. dxe6 fxe6 18. g3 Rd2 19. Bxe5) 8. dxc5 Nc6 (8... Nxc5 9. b4 Ne4 10. Bb2 Qh4 11. g3 Qh6 12. cxd5 Nd6 13. Qc7 exd5 14. Be5 Nc4 15. Qxc8+ Ke7 16. Qc5+ Ke6 17. Bf4 Qf6 18. Bh3+) 9. cxd5 {The game continues quietly, despite the unusual move.} (9. e3) (9. Nf3) 9... exd5 10. Nf3 Bf5 (10... Qa5+ 11. Bd2 Qxc5 12. Qxc5 Nxc5 13. Be3) 11. b4 O-O (11... Ng3 12. Qb2 Nxh1 13. Qxg7 Rf8 14. Bh6) (11... d4 12. g4 d3 (12... Bg6) 13. Qb2 Bxg4 14. Qxg7 Qf6 15. Qxf6 Nxf6 16. Bb2 Ke7 17. Ne5 Rhd8 18. Nxg4 Nxg4 19. Bg2 dxe2 20. Kxe2 Nxf2 21. Rhf1 Ng4 22. Bxc6 bxc6 23. h3 Nh6 24. Bf6+) 12. Bb2 (12. Qb2 d4 13. e3 d3 14. Qb3 Qf6 (14... a5) 15. Bb2 d2+ 16. Nxd2 Nxd2 17. Kxd2 Qh4 18. Ke1 Rfe8 19. Rd1 Rad8 20. Rxd8 Rxd8 21. Qc4) 12... Ng3 (12... Bg6 13. e3 Ng3 (13... b6 14. Bb5 Ne7 15. c6 Rc8 16. Qa4 Nd6 17. Rc1 Be4 18. Nd4 Nxb5 19. Qxb5) 14. Qc3 d4 15. Nxd4 Nxd4 16. hxg3) (12... d4 13. Qc4 Re8 14. Rd1 (14. Nxd4 Qf6) (14. Bxd4 Nxd4 15. Qxd4 Qe7 16. e3 Rad8 17. Qb2) 14... Qf6 15. Bxd4 Nxd4 16. Qxd4 Qe7 17. Qb2 Nxf2 18. Kxf2 Qe3+ 19. Ke1 Rad8 20. Rxd8 Rxd8 21. g4 Be4 22. Bg2 Rd3 23. Qe5 g6 24. Qg5 Qxg5 25. Nxg5 Bxg2 26. exd3 Bxh1 27. Ne4) (12... b6 13. b5 (13. g4 Bg6 14. cxb6 Qxb6 15. e3 Nxb4 16. axb4 Qxb4+ 17. Kd1 Rac8 18. Qe2 Nc3+ 19. Bxc3 Qb3+) 13... bxc5 14. bxc6 Rb8 (14... Qa5+ 15. Nd2 Rab8 (15... Ng3 16. e4) 16. c7 Rb3 (16... Qxc7 17. Nxe4 Bxe4 18. Qd2 d4) 17. Be5 (17. Rd1 c4 18. e3 Ng3 19. Qxb3 cxb3 20. hxg3)) (14... d4 15. Nd2 Rb8 16. g4 (16. Nxe4 Bxe4 17. Qd2) 16... Bg6 17. Rc1 Nc3 18. c7 Qxc7 19. e4 dxe3 20. Qxc3 exd2+ 21. Qxd2 Qb7) 15. O-O-O) (12... Re8) 13. Qc3 d4 14. Nxd4 Nxd4 {The attempt on the queen's side is countered.} 15. fxg3 Nc2+ (15... Ne6 16. e3 Qd5 17. Rd1 Qe4 18. Kf2 Rad8 19. Be2) 16. Kf2 Qg5 17. h4 (17. Rc1 Qg6 18. e3 Rfe8) 17... Qh6 (17... Qg4 18. Rc1 Rfe8 19. Rxc2 Bxc2 20. Qxc2) 18. g4 (18. Rc1 Rfe8 19. Rxc2 Bxc2 20. Qxc2 (20. e3 Rad8) 20... Qe3+ 21. Ke1 Qxg3+ 22. Kd2 Rad8+ 23. Qd3 (23. Kc1 Qe1+) 23... Rxd3+ 24. exd3 Qf2+) 18... Be4 (18... Qf4+ 19. Kg1) 19. g5 (19. Rc1 Qf4+ (19... Rfe8 20. Rh3 Rad8 21. Rxc2 Bxc2 22. Qxc2 Qf4+ 23. Rf3 (23. Kg1) 23... Qxg4 24. g3) 20. Kg1 Qe3+ 21. Qxe3 Nxe3 22. g5) 19... Qg6 20. Rd1 (20. Rc1) 20... f6 $2 (20... Rad8 21. Rd6 Rxd6 22. cxd6 Rd8 23. d7 Qf5+ 24. Kg1 f6 25. gxf6) 21. Qb3+ Kh8 22. gxf6 Rxf6+ (22... gxf6 23. Qg3) 23. Bxf6 Qxf6+ 24. Kg1 $1 Rf8 25. Rh3 $1 {Suddenly White has a strong pressure on e6.} h6 (25... Ne1 26. Rf3 (26. Rxe1 Qf2+ 27. Kh2 Qxe1) 26... Nxf3+ 27. exf3 (27. gxf3 Qg6+ 28. Kf2 Bc2)) (25... Qf2+ 26. Kh2 Ne1 27. Qg3 Qxf1 (27... Qxg3+ 28. Kxg3 Rxf1 29. Rd8+) 28. Rxe1) 26. Rf3 Bxf3 (26... Z0 27. Rxf6) 27. exf3 (27. Qxf3 Qe7 28. Rd7 Qe8) (27. gxf3 Nd4 28. Qe3 {White regains the pawn and equalises.} Rd8) (27. Qd3) (27. Qxc2) 27... Nd4 28. Qd5 Nf5 (28... Rd8 29. Qxb7 Ne2+ {lead to a difficult defence for Black.} (29... Nxf3+ $1 {Spielmann plays too ambitiously. After} 30. Qxf3 Qxf3 31. Rxd8+) 30. Bxe2 $2) 29. Qxb7 Ne3 30. Re1 Qc3 31. Re2 Qd4 32. g3 (32. Qe4 Qxe4 33. fxe4 Rxf1+) 32... Re8 (32... Nxf1+ 33. Kxf1 Qd1+ {White wins a pawn, but Black can start a counter-attack.} {The exchanges} 34. Kf2 Qh1) 33. Qa6 Rd8 (33... Ng4+ 34. Kh1 Ne3) 34. Qe6 Nxf1+ (34... Nd5+ 35. Kg2) 35. Kxf1 Qa1+ (35... Qd3 36. Kg2) 36. Kg2 {The exchange is unfavourable for Black.} Qxa3 37. Qf7 (37. c6 Qc3 38. Qe4 {also loses a pawn.} {Tactical chances offers} Rc8 $1) 37... Qxb4 (37... Qa4 38. Re6 $1 {and White wins anyway.} Qc2+ 39. Kh3 Kh7) 38. Re8+ Rxe8 39. Qxe8+ Kh7 40. Qe4+ Qxe4 41. fxe4 Kg6 42. c6 Kf6 43. c7 Ke5 44. Kf3 a5 45. c8=Q a4 46. Qc5+ Kf6 47. e5+ Kf7 48. Qd5+ Kf8 49. e6 Ke7 50. Qd7+ Kf6 51. e7 {Euwe won the match with 4-2 (+2, =2). He played too solid for Spielmann.} {A better try is} g5 $1 52. e8=Q gxh4 53. Qd4+ Kf5 54. Qf4# 1-0


