1. e4 {JvR} c6 2. d4 d5 3. f3 $5 e6 4. Bd3 c5 5. c3 Nc6 6. Ne2 Qb6 7. Bc2 Nf6 8. O-O $5 (8. e5 {JvR: '!' JvR: 'gains a plus (Mieses).'}) 8... cxd4 9. cxd4 e5 {JvR: '!?'} 10. Nbc3 exd4 11. Na4 Qc7 12. e5 $1 {JvR: 'Spielmann shows his art.' Spielmann "par excellence" !} Nd7 {JvR: '!'} (12... Ng8 $5) ({JvR: 'Nimzowitsch avoids'} 12... Qxe5 13. Re1 Be7 14. Bf4 Qh5 15. Nxd4 $40) (12... Nxe5 13. Nxd4 $40) 13. Bf4 Nc5 {JvR: '?!' This position is very difficult for Black. Diese Stellung ist sehr schwierig für Schwarz.} ({Better is} 13... d3 {JvR} 14. Bxd3 Ndxe5 15. Nd4 Bd6 16. Nb5 Qe7) 14. e6 $1 Qa5 {JvR: '!'} 15. exf7+ Kxf7 16. Nxc5 Bxc5 17. Kh1 Be6 18. a3 Qb6 19. b4 Be7 20. Qb1 (20. b5 $5 Qxb5 21. Rb1 Qa6 22. Nxd4 Nxd4 23. Qxd4 Bxa3 24. Rfe1 Qc6 25. Ba4 $40) 20... Kg8 21. b5 Na5 22. Be5 Nc4 23. Bxd4 Qc7 {JvR: '?!'} ({Counter-play gives} 23... Bc5 {JvR}) 24. Bf5 Bf7 25. Qd3 Re8 26. Rfe1 Bf8 27. Nc3 Rxe1+ 28. Rxe1 Nxa3 29. Bxg7 $3 (29. Be6 $1 Bxe6 30. Rxe6 Qf7 $16) 29... Bxg7 (29... Kxg7 $2 30. Qd4+ Kg8 31. Nxd5 $18) 30. Nxd5 Qa5 {JvR: 'A phase full of errors begins.'} (30... Bxd5 $142 31. Qxd5+ Kf8 32. Qe6 Qd8 33. Rc1 Bc3 $8 34. Qb3 Nxb5 35. Qxb5 Qe7 36. Be4 Be5 37. Bxb7 $16) 31. Ne7+ $2 ({JvR: 'Right is'} 31. Qe4 $1 Nc2 $1 (31... Nxb5 32. Be6 $18) 32. Rd1 $1 $18 {JvR: '!'} (32. Rc1 $2 Qd2 $1 33. Ne7+ Kf8 34. Qxc2 Qxc2 35. Rxc2 Kxe7 36. Rc7+ Kf6 37. Rxb7 Re8 $17) 32... Nd4 {JvR} 33. Rc1 $1 Nxf5 34. Qxf5) (31. Re8+ $5 Bxe8 32. Be6+ Bf7 33. Bxf7+ Kf8 $1 34. Qe3 Qd8 35. Bh5 Nxb5 36. Qf4+ Bf6 37. Qh6+ Bg7 38. Qf4+ $11) 31... Kf8 32. Rc1 Nc4 $1 ({Not} 32... Kxe7 $4 {JvR} 33. Qd7+ Kf6 34. Qd6+ $1) 33. Nd5 Nd6 34. Nc7 Be5 {JvR: '?'} 35. f4 {JvR: '?'} Bc4 36. Qe3 Bf6 37. Ne6+ Kf7 38. Bg4 h5 39. Ng5+ Kg7 $1 40. Bd7 Qd8 41. Ne6+ Bxe6 42. Bxe6 h4 43. Rd1 Qe7 44. Qh3 Rh6 {JvR: '?'} (44... Ne4 {(JvR) and Black wins easily.}) 45. f5 Rh5 $2 (45... Be5 $142 46. Qe3 Qf6 47. Re1 Bb2 48. Qf4 $16) 46. Qg4+ Rg5 47. Qf4 {JvR: '!'} Nf7 {JvR: '?'} 48. Rd7 Qxd7 49. Bxd7 Ne5 50. Qe4 Rg4 51. Qxb7 Ra4 52. Kg1 Ra1+ 53. Kf2 Ra2+ 54. Ke3 Kh6 55. Bc6 Kg5 56. Qh7 Ra4 57. h3 Nc4+ 58. Ke2 Kf4 59. Qh6+ Ke5 60. Qc1 Ra2+ 61. Kf3 Ra3+ 62. Kg4 Kd4 63. Kh5 Kc5 64. Qh6 Be7 65. f6 Bd6 66. f7 1-0


