{[%mdl 64]} 1. e4 e6 {Opening = C01_03 Französische Vert 4.c3 b4 / French Def 4.c3 b4} 2. d4 d5 3. Nc3 Bb4 4. exd5 exd5 5. Bd3 Nc6 6. Nge2 Nge7 7. O-O {last book move} Bf5 8. Ng3 (8. a3 Bxd3 9. Qxd3 Bxc3 10. Qxc3 O-O $11) 8... Bg6 (8... Nxd4 $143 9. Bxf5 Nexf5 10. Nxf5 Nxf5 11. Nxd5 $14) 9. Nce2 Qd7 10. f4 f5 (10... Bxd3 11. Qxd3 Bd6 12. c3 $11) 11. a3 Bd6 12. b3 Ng8 13. Bb2 Nce7 14. c4 c6 15. Qc2 {[%cal Yc4c5] White intends c5. f5 draws heavy fire} Nf6 16. Rae1 O-O 17. Kh1 Ne4 18. Ng1 b5 19. c5 (19. Nxe4 $143 fxe4 (19... dxe4 $6 20. Be2 $15) 20. Be2 bxc4 21. bxc4 Rxf4 22. Rxf4 Bxf4 $17) 19... Bc7 20. Bc1 (20. Nxe4 $143 fxe4 21. Be2 Rxf4 22. Rxf4 Bxf4 $17) 20... Ba5 21. Re3 Bc7 22. Ree1 $11 (22. Nh3 a5 $14) 22... Ba5 23. Re3 Bc7 24. Ree1 $11 (24. Nh3 a5 $14) 24... Bf7 (24... Ba5 25. Re2 $11) 25. Nf3 (25. Nxe4 $143 dxe4 26. Be2 a6 $17 (26... Qxd4 $143 27. Bb2 Qe3 28. Bd1 Qxb3 29. Qxb3 Bxb3 30. Bxb3+ Nd5 31. Ne2 $16)) 25... Be6 (25... Nxg3+ 26. hxg3 a5 27. Ne5 $11) 26. Ne5 (26. Nxe4 fxe4 27. Bxe4 dxe4 28. Qxe4 Rf6 $17) 26... Qe8 27. Ne2 (27. Nxe4 $143 dxe4 28. Be2 Nd5 $15) 27... Rf6 28. Ng1 Rh6 {Do you see the mate threat?} 29. Re3 Kh8 30. Rh3 $11 (30. Nh3 a5 $14) 30... Ng8 31. Rxh6 Nxh6 32. Nh3 $11 (32. Re1 a5 $14) 32... Bxe5 $16 (32... Nf7 $142 $5 $11) 33. fxe5 (33. dxe5 $6 Qe7 $11) 33... Nf7 34. Nf4 Nfg5 35. Be3 Bg8 36. Qe2 Ne6 37. Qh5 $11 (37. Nh3 Qg6 $16) 37... Nxf4 38. Qxe8 Rxe8 39. Bxf4 Be6 1/2-1/2


