isi di Tartakower) JvR: 'Spielmann still got the lead.  Nimzowitsch finished the publication of Mein System after the tournament. '''} Kf7 36. Nd6+ Ke7 37. Bf6+ Kxf6 38. Nxc4 $18 1-0


