{[%evp 0,53,19,9,42,-10,17,17,30,25,40,53,32,32,32,49,56,1,8,-18,-15,-17,0,0,5,1,-18,-20,87,10,17,10,4,-34,-9,-29,-13,1,-4,-3,141,210,164,172,152,195,168,168,186,148,148,513,510,510,603,618]} 1. d4 {Marin,Mihail} Nf6 2. c4 b6 3. Nc3 Bb7 4. Qc2 d5 5. cxd5 Nxd5 6. e4 Nxc3 7. bxc3 e5 8. Nf3 exd4 9. Bb5+ $1 (9. cxd4 Bb4+ {forces White to give up either the right to castle or one of the central pawns.}) 9... c6 ({I doubt that Black has full compensation for the pawn after} 9... Nd7 10. Ne5 ({Actually} 10. cxd4 Bb4+ 11. Bd2 Bxd2+ 12. Nxd2 {may also retain some slight edge.}) 10... c6 11. Bxc6 Bxc6 12. Nxc6 Qc7 13. Nxd4 Qc4 14. Qb3) 10. Bc4 (10. Be2 dxc3 11. Qxc3 Nd7 12. O-O Qc7 13. Rd1 O-O-O 14. a4 f6 15. Nd4 Nc5) 10... b5 11. Be2 (11. Rb1 Qe7 12. Bd3 dxc3 13. Qxc3 Nd7 14. O-O {Lingur,Z (2125)-Tomilova,E (2303) Voronezh 2017 (0-1, 44)}) 11... dxc3 12. Qxc3 Nd7 13. O-O Qc7 14. Bb2 Nc5 15. Qc2 Ne6 16. a4 a6 17. axb5 axb5 18. Rxa8+ Bxa8 19. Rd1 Qb7 20. Ne5 Be7 21. Bh5 Rf8 22. Qb3 g6 23. Bg4 Qc8 24. Nxf7 Kxf7 25. Qf3+ Ke8 26. Qh3 Nf4 27. Bd7+ 1-0


