1. e4 Nf6 2. Nc3 d5 3. e5 Nfd7 4. e6 {Thematic among retarding sacs - the objective is to keep your opponnent undeveloped.} fxe6 5. d4 Nf6 (5... e5 $142 6. dxe5 e6 $14) 6. Nf3 c5 7. dxc5 Nc6 8. Bb5 Bd7 9. O-O Qc7 10. Re1 h6 11. Bxc6 bxc6 12. Ne5 g5 13. Qd3 {The white squares are very weak....} Rg8 14. b4 Bg7 15. Qg6+ Kd8 16. Qf7 Be8 17. Qxe6 Rf8 18. b5 {A clearance sac} Ne4 (18... cxb5 19. Ba3) 19. Rxe4 dxe4 20. Bf4 $1 {Another clearance sac, based on the idea of d1+} Bxe5 (20... Rxf4 21. Rd1+ Bd7 22. Rxd7+ $16) 21. Bxe5 Qd7 22. Rd1 cxb5 23. Rxd7+ Bxd7 24. Qxh6 Rg8 25. c6 Be8 26. Nxb5 1-0


