1. e4 c5 2. Nf3 Nf6 3. Nc3 d5 4. exd5 Nxd5 5. d4 (5. Bc4 e6 6. O-O Be7 7. d4 (7. Re1 Nxc3 8. bxc3 O-O 9. d4 Qc7 $1) 7... Nxc3 8. bxc3 O-O 9. Ne5 Qc7 (9... Nd7) (9... Nc6) 10. Bd3 Nc6 11. Bf4 Bd6 $11) (5. Ne5 Nxc3 6. bxc3 Qc7 (6... Qd5 7. Nc4 $11) 7. Bb5+ Nd7 8. Qe2 (8. d4 cxd4 9. Qxd4 a6 10. Bxd7+ Bxd7 11. Qxd7+ Qxd7 12. Nxd7 Kxd7 $11) 8... e6 9. O-O (9. Qh5 g6 10. Qg5 Bd6 $11) 9... Bd6 10. Re1 O-O 11. d4 (11. f4 Nb6 12. g3 Bd7 $11) 11... cxd4 12. cxd4 Nxe5 13. dxe5 Bb4 14. Bd2 Bxd2 15. Qxd2 Rd8 16. Bd3 b6 17. Qf4 Bb7 18. Qh4 g6 $11 {0-1 Tarrasch,S-Tartakower,S/Berlin GER 1928 (48)}) (5. g3 Nc6 6. Bg2 Nxc3 7. bxc3 g6 8. O-O Bg7 9. a4 $6 O-O 10. Re1 Bf5 11. Ba3 b6 12. d4 Rc8 $11 {0-1 Arsenault,N-Mihok,O/Budapest 2007 (37)}) 5... Nxc3 (5... Nc6 6. dxc5 Nxc3 7. Qxd8+ Nxd8 8. bxc3 f6 9. Be3 e5 10. O-O-O Bd7 11. Nd2 Rc8 12. Ne4 Ne6 13. Rd5 Bc6 14. Nd6+ Bxd6 15. Rxd6 Ke7 16. Bc4 Nc7 17. f4 {1-0 Vallejo Pons,F-Afek,Y/France 2003/CBM 094 (33)}) (5... e6 6. Nxd5 Qxd5 7. Be3 $1 cxd4 8. Nxd4 (8. Qxd4 Qxd4 9. Nxd4 a6 10. O-O-O Bd7 11. Be2 Nc6 12. Bf3 Bc5 13. Nxc6 Bxe3+ 14. fxe3 Bxc6 15. Bxc6+ bxc6 16. Rd6 Rc8 17. Rhd1 h5 18. R1d4 Rh6 19. Rc4 Rf6 {Perlis,J-Nimzovich,A/Karlsbad 1911/0-1 (41)}) 8... a6 9. Be2 $1 Qxg2 10. Bf3 $44) 6. bxc3 g6 (6... e6 7. Bd3 Be7 8. O-O O-O $10 {Reti,R-Rubinstein,A Goteborg,1920}) 7. Be3 Bg7 8. Bb5+ Bd7 9. Bxd7+ Qxd7 $11 {[%cal Gb8c6]} (9... Nxd7 $6 10. O-O Rc8 11. Rb1 b6 12. Qe2 O-O 13. Rfd1 Qc7 14. Qa6 $1 $14 {Bogatirtschuk-Levenfisch/UdSSR/1934}) *


